<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy"
        content="default-src 'none'; style-src {{cspSource}} 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src {{cspSource}}; script-src {{cspSource}}">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{cssUri}}">
    <title>OCI DevOps Tools</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="welcomePageContainer">
        <div class="welcomePage" role="document">

            <div class="title">
                <h1>OCI DevOps Tools</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="subtitle">
                <h2>Build and Deploy Your Projects using OCI (Technology Preview)</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="links">
                    <div class="section">
                        <h2 class="caption">Project</h2>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="command:vscode.openFolder" title="Open existing Java project">Open an existing
                                    Java project</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section">
                        <h2 class="caption">Help</h2>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="vscode:extension/oracle-labs-graalvm.oci-devops"
                                    title="Open extension documentation">Extension documentation</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://github.com/oracle/gdk-vscode-extensions/issues/new?labels=enhancement"
                                    title="File a new feature request">Request a feature</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://github.com/oracle/gdk-vscode-extensions/issues/new?labels=bug"
                                    title="File a new bug report">File a bug</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://github.com/oracle/graal/discussions"
                                    title="Provide us with a feedback">Send feedback</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="docs">
                    <div class="section">
                        <h2 class="caption">Prerequisites</h2>
                        <ul>
                            <li>• Git - required for core functionality</li>
                            <li>• Java (JDK 17+)</li>
                            <li>• Kubectl - used to access applications deployed to OKE</li>
                            <li>• A Docker-API compatible container runtime such as Rancher Desktop or Docker</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section">
                        <h2 class="caption">Setup</h2>
                        <ol>
                            <li>1. <a href="https://www.oracle.com/cloud/free/"
                                    title="Create Oracle Cloud account">Create Oracle Cloud account</a> (free tier
                                supported)</li>
                            <li>2. <a href="https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/API/Concepts/sdkconfig.htm"
                                    title="Configure cloud access">Create <em>.oci/config</em></a> cloud access configuration file
                            </li>
                            <li>3. <a href="https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/API/Concepts/cliconcepts.htm"
                                    title="OCI CLI (Command Line Interface)">Install OCI CLI</a> needed for the <a
                                    href="https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/ContEng/Tasks/contengcreatingclusterusingoke_topic-Using_the_Console_to_create_a_Quick_Cluster_with_Default_Settings.htm#create-quick-cluster">OKE</a>
                                local access</li>
                            <li>4. <a
                                    href="https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/ContEng/Tasks/contengcreatingclusterusingoke.htm"
                                    title="OCI CLI (Command Line Interface)">Create and setup access to an OKE
                                    cluster</a>. OKE is Oracle's managed Kubernetes service.</li>
                            <!--li><b>!!</b> If behind a proxy, configure all the tooling accordingly</li-->
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p class="showOnStartup">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="showToolsPage" class="checkbox" {{showToolsPage}}>
                    <label for="showToolsPage" class="checkboxLabel">Show this page when using OCI DevOps Tools</label>
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="{{jsUri}}"></script>

</body>
